text: Vladimir Banjanac (born 13 October 1966) is a Serbian rower. He competed at the 1988 Summer Olympics and the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Yugoslavia Category:Olympic rowers as Independent Olympic Participants Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
